title: "Sonic the Hedgehog 3"
rating: 0.1
review {
  direction {
    director {
      name: "Jeff Fowler"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The direction on a macroscale is pretty fun as they create this gaming action-comedy that is pretty true to the Sonic games; the direction on a microscale is decent as it has the silly comedy moments Sonic is known for, and tackles some darker, more mature themes that you do not see as much from a family movie; the storytelling is what you would expect from a family movie"
  }
