      comments: "Plays the gritty nature of Shadow well; basically just John Wick, but Shadow"
    }
    cast {
      rating: "Decent"
      comments: "Typical family movie background character performances; help with establishing the tone and making the movie silly fun"
    }
    rating: "Decent to Pretty Good"
  }
  story {
    writer {
      name: "Pat Casey"
    }
    writer {
      name: "Josh Miller"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The concept is a continuation of the Sonic the Hedgehog story, with the added Shadow storyline that is true to the video games, particularly 'Sonic Adventure 2'; the plot structure is pretty simple; character writing captures the essense of these characters that is true to the video games"
  }
  screenplay {
    writer {
      name: "Pat Casey"
    }
    writer {
      name: "Josh Miller"
    }
    writer {
      name: "John Whittington"
    }
    rating: "Decent to Pretty Good"
    comments: "The dialogue is pretty and family oriented, but does get a little bit mature at points; the humor is very silly and meta, so what you would expect from both Sonic the Hedgehog and Jim Carrey; the symbolism is somewhat there as the movie touches on familial themes and loss; the foreshadowing is pretty standard because you kinda expect where this movie is going because its made for families"
  }
  score {
