      name: "Tom Holkenborg"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Helps establish the tones and does a decent job incorporating classic Sonic themes"
  }
  soundtrack {
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Enjoyed how they included 'Live and Learn' as an homage to 'Sonic Adventure 2'"
  }
  cinematography {
    cinematographer {
      name: "Brandon Trost"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Standard for an action-comedy of this scale"
  }
  editing {
    editor {
      name: "Al LeVine"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Pretty sound"
  }
  sound {
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "Helped make the action-comedy what it is"
  }
  visual_effects {
    rating: "Good"
    comments: "Helped mesh the Sonic character's with the environment as the overall feel makes the movie look like it's in the Sonic universe"
  }
  costumes {
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "Helps make the Roboniks look like their video game characters"
  }
  pacing: "Pacing is a little on the faster side, but there really isn't that much plot to go through"
  climax: "Climax is pretty cool as it pays homage to 'Sonic Adventure 2'"
  tone: "Tone is silly, family comedy that makes this feel like its something from the Sonic franchise"
  final_notes: "Really enjoyed the homages to the Sonic franchise and 'Sonic Adventure 2'"
  overall: "Overall, a pretty good family comedy that is carried by its silly humor, action sequences, and performances from Jim Carrey, Ben Schwartz, and Keanu Reeves as the movie pays homage to the Sonic franchise, particularly 'Sonic Adventure 2'"
